snippet.title: Forest Reigns by VG Entertainment: Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Forest Reigns is a survival FPS set in post-apocalyptic Paris overrun by a mutant forest and its deadly creatures. Adapt to use the ever-changing environment in your favor. Craft weapons, bond with factions and explore the world freely, but watch your back. The choices you make will shape the story.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3325070/Forest_Reigns 

Forest Reigns website: https://forestreigns.com/ 
VG Entertainment website: https://vgentertainment.com/
